The paper deals with delay-optimal control and user scheduling for downlink coordinated MIMO systems with energy harvesting capability. This involves the use of information theory, networking, control systems, and optimization techniques, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MA, and cs.DC. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
